      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "URANA SPACE (8) has hit the frame at seven of 19 starts and has won two of last three, the latest scoring (37.43) over 643m at Gawler. Performs well off this draw. Drawn wide but with a clean break will be tough to beat again. NITROUS (4) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and two placings from six starts. Below best last time at this track (43.84) in a Grade 5/6, finishing a 11 length fourth. Looks suited here and can measure up. OREGON JANET (5) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 10 length win at this track in a handy 43.11. Awkwardly drawn but has a good record over this journey. Hard to fault her form and she makes plenty of appeal. CANYA VIVI (1) was in the money again last start when third at this track (43.69).",
